    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="muted">Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString()}</p>

    <p>
      Amicbridge respects your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect,
      use, store, and protect personal information when you use our website and services.
    </p>

    <h2>1. What Amicbridge does</h2>
    <p>
      Amicbridge provides <strong>educational information and strategy frameworks</strong>
      related to crypto investment planning. We do not provide regulated financial advice,
      do not manage funds, and do not guarantee outcomes.
    </p>

    <h2>2. Information we collect</h2>
    <p>When you submit a request, we may collect:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Your name and email address</li>
      <li>High-level financial goals and preferences</li>
      <li>Investment-related information you choose to share</li>
    </ul>

    <p>
      Please <strong>do not</strong> submit sensitive information such as passwords,
      private keys, seed phrases, bank logins, or full identification numbers.
    </p>

    <h2>3. How we use your information</h2>
    <p>Your information is used to:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Review and respond to your request</li>
      <li>Provide educational strategy information</li>
      <li>Communicate with you about your request or service</li>
      <li>Improve our website and service quality</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>4. Payment for services</h2>
    <p>
      Amicbridge offers paid educational services. After reviewing your request,
      you may receive a <strong>payment link</strong> from Amicbridge if you choose
      to proceed.
    </p>

    <p>
      Payment is for <strong>educational information and strategy frameworks only</strong>.
      Payment does not guarantee results, profits, or financial outcomes.
    </p>

    <h2>5. How payments work</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Payment is requested only after you submit a request</li>
      <li>Payment is optional and not required to submit a request</li>
      <li>Payment links are sent directly by Amicbridge</li>
      <li>No payment details are stored on this website</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>6. Data sharing</h2>
    <p>
      We do not sell your personal data. Your information may be shared only with:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Email and form service providers used to deliver responses</li>
      <li>Payment providers used to process transactions (if applicable)</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>7. Data storage and security</h2>
    <p>
      We take reasonable steps to protect your information. However, no online system
      is 100% secure. You submit information at your own risk.
    </p>

    <h2>8. Your rights</h2>
    <p>
      You may request access to, correction of, or deletion of your personal data
      by contacting us.
    </p>

    <h2>9. Third-party services</h2>
    <p>
      Amicbridge may use third-party services (such as form processors or payment providers).
      We are not responsible for the privacy practices of external services.
    </p>

    <h2>10. Changes to this policy</h2>
